components.label: Content
components.content:
PADI Dive Centers and Resorts are able to secure professional liability insurance for the dive professionals who provide professional services for the store at reduced prices. Discount rates 
are computed according to the gross receipts for instructional and supervisory activities. PADI Members with multiple locations should include the receipts for all facilities.

components.label: Content
components.content:
1. Additional Insureds are only added if required by written contract.
  2. No charge for Additional Insureds, however, all must be listed.
  3. Entities other than those mentioned, when listed, will be reviewed by the insurance carrier; inclusion on your Certificate of Insurance will indicate that coverage is in effect.
  4. List business relationship versus personal relationship; eg., "Bob Smith, property owner" not "Bob Smith, father".
  5. Other Instructors and assistants may not be Additional Insureds but must obtain their own insurance.

components.content:
We (I) know and acknowledge that this policy does not provide any insurance coverage or defense
 for snow-ski rentals or snow-ski binding adjustments. No coverage is provided for firearms (this exclusion does not include spear guns). No coverage is provided under 
this policy for any professional liability except under the terms of the Contingent Professional 
Liability coverage. Professional Liability includes, but is not limited to, instruction of scuba
 diving and snorkeling or other forms of aquatic activity. The policy defines these and other
 exclusions as they apply. Burglary Coverage is afforded only with a working Central S
tation Alarm (Policy Warranty and applies only when property coverage is purchased). 
This policy does not provide coverage for Workers Compensation, Employers Liability, 
Employment Practices Liability, motorized watercraft or non motorized watercraft 
more than 20 feet in length.

components.label: Content

Upon receipt and review of the completed application, Vicencia & Buckley,

your approval before coverage is placed. Upon your acceptance of the policy and premium, credit card information can be provided to Vicencia & Buckley, 
a division of HUB International or a check/money order mailed. Premium 
Financing is also available.
